{
  "id": "adv_event_2601_01_04",
  "title": "仲良し三人組\nと友情破壊\nゲーム",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか……私達の素を、表に出すつもりなの？\nお互い大嫌いだけど、仕方なく一緒にいるだけだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 11.377346611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……マジかよ\nよりにもよってあんたが、そんなこと言い出すとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5706798871,
      "endTime": 17.0973692258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.5706798871
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.3040359497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。私は本気よ\n――ゲーム配信をやりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3040359497,
      "endTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――12月27日　深夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.314170742,
      "endTime": 25.314170742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『【実況】仲良し三人組で友情破壊ゲームを遊ぶ』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.314170742,
      "endTime": 27.2741705894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.2741705894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　って訳で、ゲーム機も準備したところで\nこれから、すごろくゲームを遊んでいこうと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1008373578,
      "endTime": 35.7728099187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.9594766617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ルーレットを回して、マスを進みながら\n人生のいろんなイベントをこなしてくゲームだね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9594766617,
      "endTime": 42.8352360726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ。最終的に、一番資産が多い人が勝ちなのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0285691579,
      "endTime": 48.2685692151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.4752357483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "でもこのゲーム、「もしかすると友情が壊れるかも」\nなんて解説に書いてあるんだけど……大丈夫かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4752357483,
      "endTime": 58.075235939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.261902682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "あら。貴方達のことは信頼しているけど、それはそれ\nゲームは本気でやらなきゃ、面白くないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.261902682,
      "endTime": 66.3922883671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.5856216431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "それに『友情破壊ゲーム』なんて言われても\nそもそも私達には、友情なんて存在しないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5856216431,
      "endTime": 72.925621605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "お？　二人とも、もうやる気満々じゃない\nそれじゃ早速、キャラ作成から始めていきましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1256217004,
      "endTime": 80.8835579874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.1256217004
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.9302255631
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_roulette-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 82.1968852362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "よっしゃ、億ション買っちゃえ億ション\n借金しても、多分ターンが進めば返せるだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9968852362,
      "endTime": 90.2996289572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ヤバっ、トラブルのマス踏んだ\nいやあああ、いきなり悪霊に取り憑かれた！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4996290526,
      "endTime": 96.96722539279999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_quiz-no-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2567.036215300007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.4996290526
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.1805585545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはここでアイドルに就職、っと\nこのためにずっとパラメータ上げてきたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1805585545,
      "endTime": 104.06949297599999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_roulette-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 104.2694930714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほらfranちゃ～ん、kanaのサインあげる\nきっと高値が付くから、大事にしててね～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2694930714,
      "endTime": 112.27901674920001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.4856835684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "だ、誰があんたのサインなんか……\nお宝ありがと～、kana",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4856835684,
      "endTime": 117.8330759367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "で、mihoはとにかくデートマス狙いね……\n合コンしたがるmihoとか、意外過ぎて怖いんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.0464091938,
      "endTime": 127.2316697758,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_roulette-01.m4a",
          "delay": 940.2560740999917
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_roulette-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4220.2560740999925
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.0464091938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "早めに結婚して、相手の収入と子供の仕送りを足せば\n私一人で稼ぐより、資産を増やせるもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4250030519,
      "endTime": 135.12967424410002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.4250030519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "そういう戦略もあるとは思うけどさぁ\n家族を金づるとしか思ってない感が凄いね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3163407964,
      "endTime": 142.44477621739998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_roulette-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6828.435420999995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.3163407964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳で、早速子供が生まれたわ\n二人とも、ご祝儀をちょうだいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.658109379,
      "endTime": 148.46810960789998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.658109379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ただでさえ利息持っていかれてるのに\nご祝儀まで払わないといけないの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6814430556,
      "endTime": 153.5804454168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.6814430556
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.6871188482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_04-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "これで全員ゴールしたかな？\nさ～て、最終的な資産総額は…………と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
